title: Maldives Central Bank Balance Sheet
description: Central Bank Balance Sheet in Maldives decreased to 21002.80 MVR Million in September from 22746.30 MVR Million in August of 2022. Central Bank Balance Sheet in Maldives averaged 13001.09 MVR Million from 2004 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 26178 MVR Million in December of 2020 and a record low of 3800.45 MVR Million in October of 2004. This page provides - Maldives Central Bank Balance Sheet- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Maldives Monetary Authority
